Dear Ben and Bert

Thanks very much for the interesting discussion

Yes that why I was additionally using compareRaster(r1,r2) and then resample (r2, r1) to adapt the extend.

library(raster)
r1 <- raster("")
r2 <- raster("f")
compareRaster(r1, r2)

extent(r1)
extent(r2)

r2_resampled <- resample(r2, r1)
compareRaster(r1, r2_resampled)

CompareRaster:
Evaluate whether a two or more Raster* objects have the same extent, number of rows and columns, projection, resolution, and origin (or a subset of these comparisons).

Kind regards
Sibylle

